The evidence with the title 'Low oil prices prove how wrong Obama was yet again | New York Post ' says Mar 18, 2017  ... No, there are no guarantees: if the global economy heats up and supplies can't keep pace, prices will rise. But with all the new US drilling, America is now better poised to meet new demand and keep those prices in check. It sure is a good thing Obama was right about Americans' intelligence. 
